  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/46f37009e075e12e66fe838e35589d66.poster.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/46f37009e075e12e66fe838e35589d66.webm?t=1757956140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/46f37009e075e12e66fe838e35589d66.mp4?t=1757956140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defend your shrine against humanity as the last, and oh-so-vengeful god in this turn-based roguelike strategy game. Each run presents new challenges and opportunities to expand your reservoir of spells and summons against the blasphemous mortals who slaughtered every god in existence… except you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/e38923864ab4b39eaa674cd75393f501.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=103 /></span><br>Each turn, manage your resources to turn the tides of randomly-generated battles in your favor and protect your shrine at all costs.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Will you summon <strong>auto-battling units</strong> that attack, buff, or heal?<br></li><li>Will you <strong>cast spells</strong> to resurrect, enchant or poison targets?<br></li><li>Will you <strong>terraform the map</strong> with tiles that boost, block or teleport units? </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/a979f5986e2e563b724cce0d444cefb0.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=103 /></span><br>Between battles, choose your path and upgrades wisely to find the optimal synergetic build for your next fight. Discover hundreds of items in four different elemental classes to create unique builds each run!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/467fad3942a2f47d779b94e1ac5e84b4.poster.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/467fad3942a2f47d779b94e1ac5e84b4.webm?t=1757956140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/467fad3942a2f47d779b94e1ac5e84b4.mp4?t=1757956140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/a8a950a384fb7e7d492068eea4fce27d.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=103 /></span><br>Unlock permanent upgrades after each run to destroy the ten continents and decide the fate of the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/a26e4013dfff59cda211378f828f8efe.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=228 /></span>",
