ifferent elemental classes to create unique builds each run!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/467fad3942a2f47d779b94e1ac5e84b4.poster.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/467fad3942a2f47d779b94e1ac5e84b4.webm?t=1757956140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/467fad3942a2f47d779b94e1ac5e84b4.mp4?t=1757956140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/a8a950a384fb7e7d492068eea4fce27d.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=103 /></span><br>Unlock permanent upgrades after each run to destroy the ten continents and decide the fate of the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677090/extras/a26e4013dfff59cda211378f828f8efe.avif?t=1757956140\" width=616 height=228 /></span>",
